{"tid":531486,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"城市足印 - 徐小鳳","createTime":"2018-01-17T01:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T09:50:31.000Z","uid":167050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a458bec78dab63584b7bc17835b3b27ccbae64f3","tid":531486,"uid":167050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:19:03.000Z","msg":"徐小鳳 <br />\n<br />\n城市足印<br />\n<br />\n作詞：小華<br />\n作曲：林敏怡<br />\n<br />\n留心街中每個人　彼此匆匆過<br />\n皺著眉心　重疊的足印　細踏了千遍<br />\n多千遍　看落也不要緊<br />\n<br />\n留心身邊每個人　冷冷的雙眼<br />\n試問何因　人在匆匆裡　那曾知道<br />\n今天你我是遠還是近<br />\n<br />\n如今都市內每人<br />\n彷彿不可以讓友情接近<br />\n時間鞭策著的一生<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=fb50a833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n天天相見卻沒有時間望人<br />\n<br />\n留心街中這個人<br />\n帶笑一雙眼　那樣誠懇<br />\n迎面的走過　對著我一笑<br />\n心中愛意自遠而近<br />\n<br />\n陽光溫暖像這人<br />\n一顆心充滿著友情歡欣<br />\n人生相見瞬即相分<br />\n能否再讓兩心可以漸近<br />\n<br />\n最近有歌星在電視唱這歌曲,為什麼听到後有一種傷心的感覺呢!"},{"pid":"f06e6399875e2813cb0c8daf41fb2516b241209c","tid":531486,"uid":167050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:21:21.000Z","msg":"《城市足印》由香港著名歌手徐小凤演唱，小华作词，林敏怡作曲，收录于1986年《每一步》[1]  专辑，由宝丽金唱片公司出版，是香港TVB电视剧《流氓大亨》主题曲。<br />\n<br />\n32年前了."},{"pid":"b3e5732593999f7f86a2ad538b831c848da9f3a0","tid":531486,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8abd475b57903b4744601ccdd978768eb34c7c3b","tid":531486,"uid":167050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y6cjhn7K3QI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY6cjhn7K3QI&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=52a4ffea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y6cjhn7K3QI</a>"},{"pid":"5e710ecd18846882605fc1085cf7652634074554","tid":531486,"uid":167050,"like":1,"dis